data.description: This Roomy Cul-de-Sac home has 4 Bedroom plus a study. The home has been updated with NEW CARPET AND FRESH PAINT! Snuggle with your loved ones in the large living Room with high ceilings in front of the fireplace. The kitchen has granite counter tops, gas range, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar and is open to the living room.  Downstairs' master suite features double vanities, soaking tub and large walk in closet! Three large bedrooms and 2 full baths upstairs with a large living area that overlooks the living room.  Spacious Backyard has Covered Patio. This home also features tons of natural light throughout the home with very large windows.
